SUMMARY:There Is No Easy Mode: Video Game Trivia
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:Think you know all there is to know about those gosh-darn vide
 o games?! PROVE IT!! Assemble a group of your fellow gamers\, or play solo
 \, for a chance to answer a gauntlet of progressively difficult video game
  trivia questions\, claim cool Canadian snack prizes\, and earn the title 
 of Trivia Champion of VGM CON 2025! Asking trivia questions from all eras 
 of gaming\, There Is No Easy Mode has a variety of question formats includ
 ing audio\, video and picture questions\, and more than a few tricky traps
  from our host MooMan. 
END:VEVENT
