SUMMARY:Beginning Conducting Workshop
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:Learn the basics of conducting live musicians with Jamin Morde
 n\, the music director for the Washington Metropolitan Gamer Symphony Orch
 estra. This workshop will use excerpts and short VGM songs to cover simple
  ideas such as easy beat patterns\, providing cues\, and maintaining tempo
 s. Time permitting\, we might also get into more advanced techniques (cuto
 ffs and expressive decisions).  
END:VEVENT
