SUMMARY:Breath of the Wild Anew: Intro to Bingos
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:Do you love Breath of the Wild\, but playing it feels stale? C
 ome bring your switch as Katie tells you about Breath of the Wild bingos a
 nd help you set up a bingo file so your adventures in Hyrule never have to
  end. 
END:VEVENT
