SUMMARY:OC ReMix: 25 years of VGM Arrangements!
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:The OC ReMix community has showcased 4\,600+ game music ReMixe
 s since launching in 1999. With rock\, jazz\, funk\, electronic\, and so m
 uch more\, come experience OCR's unique & creative VGM arrangements! Come 
 join the judges and staff of OverClocked ReMix and learn just how many way
 s talented musicians interpret the game music they love! 
END:VEVENT
