SUMMARY:The Bruce Lees of Fighting Games
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:Fei Long? Marshall Law? Liu Kang? There are dozens of Bruce Le
 e clones in fighting games but thereâ€™s even more Asian cinema influ
 ence in video games that you may not know of! Join the hosts of the Heroes
  Three Podcast as they explore Asian film and its influence on video games
 . Discover the secret origins of some of your favorite characters\, stages
 \, and music! 
END:VEVENT
