SUMMARY:Dwelling of Duels: Tornado of Solos LP!
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:Dwelling of Duels has been around for more than 20 years\, ser
 ving up monthly VGM competitions that anyone can participate in. While eve
 ry month generally has a theme that allows for a wide variety of songs to 
 be rearranged\, we're doing things differently here. For VGM Con\, we're h
 osting a special contest\, the Tornado of Solos\, where everyone has to ta
 ke on the SAME tune. 
END:VEVENT
