SUMMARY:Arranging for Brass Quintet: A Live Demonstration
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:The Game Brass will be talking about the ins and outs of arran
 ging for brass instruments\, specifically for small ensemble groups like t
 hemselves. While presenting facts and fielding questions\, one of our memb
 ers will be arranging (in real-time) an audience-suggested piece\, which T
 he Game Brass will perform at the end of the panel. 
