SUMMARY:VGM SPECIFICALLY is Good for your Mental Health
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:VGM DJ/Producer and Mental Health activist Theology takes you 
 through a journey to prove that video game music /specifically/ is good fo
 r your mental health. Using various scholarly sources and examples from hi
 s life\, come along and sharpen your critical thinking skills both as indi
 viduals and as a community alike. 
END:VEVENT
