SUMMARY:Streaming a 150-Member Orchestra with WMGSO
LOCATION:Panels 2/Conference Room D
DESCRIPTION:In this panel\, WMGSO Twitch Leadership “Ashleah\, David\, F
 abio\, and Jarel“provide a glimpse behind the curtain to share what it r
 eally takes to livestream video game orchestra performances. We'll cover d
 ifferent setup scenarios\, processes for coordinating with performance ven
 ues\, necessary equipment\, and how to fund it all on a nonprofit communit
 y orchestra budget. 
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9ee44a5658121127be678dbaae5c0787
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20250328T000000Z
DTSTART:20250413T130000
