SUMMARY:Odd Meters in VGM
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we dive into the fascinating world of odd meters in
  video game music! This panel explores how irregular rhythms ”measures t
 hat don't fit into standard duple\, triple\, or compound meters”are used
  as powerful narrative devices to convey emotions such as lightheartedness
 \, oddity\, unfamiliarity\, and panic. 
END:VEVENT
