SUMMARY:How To Make Non-Corny Nerdcore with Joey Z
LOCATION:Panels 1/Conference Room E
DESCRIPTION:Joey makes rap music that many people regrettably describe as 
 "nerdcore". Joey thinks that basically everybody who makes nerdcore sucks 
 at making rap music. Joey would like to explain to you how to make music t
 hat will be described as "nerdcore"\, while also making music that Joey wo
 uld not describe as "unlistenable" 
END:VEVENT
